headline: GRAZA GOES GLASS: LEADING OLIVE OIL BRAND EXPANDS FORMAT OFFERINGS FOR DRIZZLE & SIZZLE
summary: Graza, the cult-favorite olive oil brand and pantry staple, is thrilled to announce the launch of its first-ever glass bottles for the Drizzle and Sizzle duo. Joining the brand's beloved squeeze bottles and "beer can" refills, this launch gives consumers more ways to enjoy the same fresh, single-origin olive oil in a new format. Starting today, the glass bottles are available online at graza.co and rolling out in Whole Foods Market and Kroger stores nationwide.
